phrases: And that is my little sister, Ruri.

but she eventually said I am not enough like a prince.

Okay, let us go with that.

Please forgive me for only being able to convey my love like this.

I was still immature as a princess, too.

Hey, how about you come with us and-

Now slowly move up the camera.

So I am making my own PV.

No, she is a self proclaimed idol,
so I think she is usually a normal person that you would see walking down the street.

This shining cuteness of mine is all that is needed for me to dazzle!
It is just too much fun!

You can make some cash in a flea market.

Is it going to be amazing?

You do not have any say on-

What was that old man doing?

Then that person that ran into her was...

But, this is a rare group.
They have not realized that it is him?
I guess I will keep it quiet, then.

Maybe because she was about to drop something important?
If so, we will look for it together.
You should not be like that, Aoi-chan.
They are no friends of mine!

It is no different at all.
We like people who say what is on their mind.
Shiroyan really is a genuine idiot.
Kurotatsu is a hardcore freak, too.
It is really hard to be with them.

We need to search for what you dropped before it gets dark.

I will let you guys be my slaves.
